actions.title: Support Commands
actions.description:
Here you can see a tutorial for the support commands:

**You have two ways to open a support ticket. Either make "=t" or you press the button where it says "open ticket".**

If you make a ticket via command, you can also write your reason behind the command. For example: "**+t** `I found an error!`"
